(1, 'Jul 23rd, 2017 10:02:18 AM', 1, 'Filler', 'testing news comments\n\nalso using mysqli string escaping when inserting the news content into the database\n\nalso uses nl2br() when displaying the news content from the database onto the actual news.php page\n\nhopefully this works like i wanted it to, but i suppose we\'ll just have to wait and see'),
(2, 'Aug 8th, 2017 2:26:05 PM', 1, 'Pokemon Absolute: Open Beta', 'Hello and welcome to the beta stage of Pokemon Absolute!\r\n\r\nIt\'s been a long time coming, but the game has finally reached the point of completion where a beta stage is necessary. There\'s quite a few features that are currently ready for testing, and I\'d love to see what you\'re able to find, as well as whether or not the feature appeals to you and what you think of it, whether negative or positive. If you like how a certain feature works, that\'s great; tell me what you like about it! However, if you don\'t like how a particular feature works, please let me know what your thoughts are, whether it\'s adjusting the feature a little bit, or even completely reworking the feature; I\'m all ears and am ready to listen to what you have to say!\r\n\r\nThe game has been in development for quite a few months, as <b>Ephenia</b> and <b>I</b> have been working nearly day in and day out to iron out features, get them working, and then testing them out to make sure they\'re balanced and <i>hopefully</i> fully operational, for you guys!\r\n\r\nExpect a ton of updates to come out in the near future, as well as some surprises for you guys!\r\n\r\nHere\'s a link to the feedback page, where you may tell us how you feel about certain features of the RPG!\r\n<b><a href=\'feedback_form.php\'>Feedback Form</a></b>\r\n\r\nWith Much Appreciation and Sincerity,\r\n<b><a href=\'profile.php?id=1\'>Toxocious</a></b> and <b><a href=\'profile.php?id=2\'>Ephenia</a></b>');
